The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Metro Briefs

n Ranjit Singh, a private security guard, was arrested in Chhapra, Bihar, on Saturday for being part of the gang that looted Rs 32.5 lakh from NGO employees a couple of weeks ago.

n Chandrani Roychowdhury, 29, a resident of Mahestala, on the southern fringes, was arrested on Sunday after her husband Bhaskar, 32, was found dead in their house.

n R. Singh, 31, and J. Singh, 22, residents of Hoshiarpur, in Punjab, were arrested at the airport on Sunday for forging their passports. They went to Bangkok and Cambodia last month. They had planned to go to the UK via Dubai, according to police.




